3. Data Retention and Deletion
We do not personally store any of your data on our own servers. However, since we use Google services, you can manage your advertising preferences and data through your Android device settings (Google > Ads).

4. Children’s Privacy
This app is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.

